Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.23,0:03:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論怎樣的垃圾隊伍  都能使其獲勝的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.44,0:03:53.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天才經理人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.48,0:03:56.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初  初次見面  我是倉部勝代
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.60,0:04:03.45,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倉部勝代  天才經理人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.18,0:04:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丈途
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.34,0:04:21.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這  這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.97,0:04:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  之後就交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.39,0:04:26.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部  部長
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.56,0:04:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎來到罐頭小屋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.10,0:04:33.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何  都只剩下最後48小時
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.94,0:04:35.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,截稿日期已經不能再推遲了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.15,0:04:37.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.70,0:04:40.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是一定沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.45,0:04:42.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我相信芥川老師
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.58,0:04:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.12,0:04:51.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊  文科系不是這樣打氣的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.13,0:04:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.04,0:04:54.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我弄錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.96,0:04:53.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.92,0:04:56.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這個笨蛋笨蛋笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.46,0:04:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係啦  沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.72,0:05:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢  雖然是低潮期
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.64,0:05:03.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也不能一味消沉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.35,0:05:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芥川老師
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.85,0:05:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要打起精神  噢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.22,0:05:10.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  我一直都只是幫運動部打氣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.69,0:05:13.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文科系是第一次所以稍稍有點不安
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.23,0:05:16.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芥川老師
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.98,0:05:18.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.69,0:05:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別叫我老師了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.24,0:05:22.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我丈途就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.95,0:05:25.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也請叫我勝代吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.62,0:05:26.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  小勝代
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.16,0:05:28.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.87,0:05:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管事情來龍去脈如何  她是在幫我打氣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.50,0:05:36.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說是部長帶來的  有點那個啥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.55,0:05:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼請坐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.05,0:05:43.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原稿紙和筆都準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.09,0:05:46.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼需要的話儘管和我說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.96,0:05:55.90,Comment,NTP,0000,0110,0120,,{\fad(600,0)\an3\3c#000000\bord3.5}中午12點 : 2小時過後
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.58,0:06:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我先去換衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.29,0:06:16.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,換  換衣服?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.63,0:06:19.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在  在那扇門的後面…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.64,0:06:30.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這  這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.73,0:06:33.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  還是想不出
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.73,0:06:36.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平時的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.48,0:06:39.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要這種程度就能寫20頁原稿的說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.69,0:06:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之要快點寫出來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.07,0:06:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,專欄  連載  直接發表新作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.57,0:06:45.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.78,0:06:48.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦  如果就這樣一直寫不出來的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.29,0:06:57.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,L O V E  芥川!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.83,0:07:01.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,C U T E  丈途!  Yeah～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.30,0:07:03.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很高興  但麻煩你安靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.29,0:07:07.80,Comment,NTP,0000,0110,0120,,{\fad(600,0)\an3\3c#000000\bord3.5}下午1點 : 3小時過後
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.68,0:07:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人聽說了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.60,0:07:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.47,0:07:13.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於芥川丈途啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.56,0:07:16.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為截稿日期快到了所以請假了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.81,0:07:21.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像聽說因為低潮而被監禁在罐頭小屋了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.86,0:07:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他請假後清靜多了也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.45,0:07:28.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便也給我變成正常人多好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.57,0:07:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,監禁?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.17,0:07:45.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  之前一直認為制服圍裙這種著裝很普通
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.30,0:07:47.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來應該改變一下這觀念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.34,0:07:48.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丈途同學
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.18,0:07:51.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午飯很快就做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.35,0:07:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請等一下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.47,0:07:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.98,0:08:05.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.44,0:08:06.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.74,0:08:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經好了?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.45,0:08:10.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太快了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.95,0:08:12.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.08,0:08:15.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是第一次吃女生親手做的料理
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.83,0:08:18.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要多吃點  補充體力哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.25,0:08:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.17,0:08:21.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  趁熱吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.71,0:08:23.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.80,0:08:28.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常補腦的勝代特製金槍魚眼珠湯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.63,0:08:31.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  請吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.56,0:08:37.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丈途同學
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.56,0:08:39.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  丈途同學
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.39,0:08:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丈途同學!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.77,0:08:44.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勝代君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.28,0:08:45.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.36,0:08:48.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人身上在某種條件下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.19,0:08:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能變大6倍左右的器官是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.24,0:08:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.37,0:08:54.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男  男性生殖…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.78,0:08:58.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢貨  注意你的發言
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.91,0:09:00.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.92,0:09:01.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是瞳孔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.08,0:09:03.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在黑暗的地方會變大
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.84,0:09:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在黑暗的地方?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.04,0:09:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.84,0:09:08.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就來對下答案
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.39,0:09:18.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.35,0:09:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來夏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.27,0:09:21.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然還有時間打瞌睡  你還真是從容啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.65,0:09:24.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是在趕稿嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.27,0:09:28.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕  睡了好久
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.32,0:09:30.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你叫醒我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.20,0:09:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不抓緊的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.45,0:09:33.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要在意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.61,0:09:35.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是來拍寫不出
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.74,0:09:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工口小說的色情作家的照片而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.58,0:09:40.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  丈途同學
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.12,0:09:43.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倉部勝代啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.13,0:09:44.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.63,0:09:46.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子餓了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.96,0:09:49.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  我去準備晚飯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.51,0:09:50.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.38,0:09:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丈途
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.80,0:09:53.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道她是誰嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.22,0:09:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天才經理人對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.14,0:09:58.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是被打氣的人絕對會獲勝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.18,0:10:02.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確  有她打氣就可以說是獲得了勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.27,0:10:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那個勝利無論何時都伴隨著代價
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.99,0:10:13.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是勝代應援的棒球部的悲慘下場
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.49,0:10:19.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我的手機  怎麼會在…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.04,0:10:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.16,0:10:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.21,0:10:24.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36}等…等下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.92,0:10:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是丈途老師的經理人  叫倉部勝代
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.29,0:10:30.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找丈途老師嗎  請稍候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.09,0:10:33.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是編輯先生打來的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.51,0:10:36.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在  說我不在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.55,0:10:38.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他讓我說他不在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.14,0:10:41.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.77,0:10:43.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不是這樣的  請聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.85,0:10:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是電腦突然出了點問題…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.52,0:10:46.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊不  我是用手寫的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.19,0:10:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我的家人去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.90,0:10:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拍到好的照片了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.86,0:10:57.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你就加油趕稿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.12,0:11:00.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經夠了  我不幹了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.83,0:11:00.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36}丈途同學
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.41,0:11:01.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我根本沒有寫作的才能
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.95,0:11:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,編輯其實也是這麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.16,0:11:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有這種事  丈途同學你一定能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.50,0:11:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請找回自信
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.75,0:11:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.29,0:11:11.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這隻手的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.38,0:11:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因為它
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.30,0:11:14.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害我非寫原稿不可
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.84,0:11:15.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36}丈  丈途同學  不能這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.68,0:11:17.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才會有截稿日期啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.67,0:11:56.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  這種時間她還在努力著
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.43,0:11:59.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也稍微  再努力下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.14,0:12:01.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.01,0:12:03.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手丈途同學
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.10,0:12:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丈途同學!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.74,0:12:25.33,Comment,NTP,0000,0110,0120,,{\fad(600,0)\an3\3c#000000\bord3.5}上午8點 : 22小時過後
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.44,0:12:43.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 騙人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.44,0:12:47.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用不著勉強自己讀我的小說啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.42,0:12:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  作為經理人必須
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.04,0:12:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解丈途同學所有的作品
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.36,0:12:55.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  不會吧  不要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.32,0:13:00.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別  別過來…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.74,0:13:05.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到她居然叫了一晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.74,0:13:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要認輸  加油  盡全力…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.60,0:13:13.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然做夢都在為我加油我很高興啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.17,0:13:17.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好 我也睏了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.27,0:13:18.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丈途
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.24,0:13:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從來夏那裡聽說了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.51,0:13:22.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說你和經理人都被關起來…了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.51,0:13:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  律  不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.22,0:13:27.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天能不能也幫我請個假
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.73,0:13:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間實在是緊得不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.50,0:13:33.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緊…緊?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.45,0:13:36.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  真的是太緊了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.41,0:13:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忙著趕稿脫不開身啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.23,0:13:38.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36}難…難不成
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.58,0:13:39.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脫不開身?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.58,0:13:39.63,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雁字搦め:一種捆綁方法 引申為被事物纏身 不能自由行動之意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.26,0:13:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以…以你的才能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.76,0:13:43.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許會有這種想法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.61,0:13:45.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我我我我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.01,0:13:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,律 快背圓周率
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.28,0:13:55.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3.141592653589793238462633832795…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.01,0:13:54.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36}不行了 我要睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.95,0:14:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勝代君
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.73,0:14:01.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.09,0:14:05.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,位於加拿大薩斯喀徹溫省北部的湖的名字是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.62,0:14:08.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.86,0:14:10.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,O Oman…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.02,0:14:11.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說清楚點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.29,0:14:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oman…Lake
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.27,0:14:13.24,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這湖的日語發音就和小穴(omanko)發音一樣 勝代迫於無奈才改用E文
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.42,0:14:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再大聲點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.15,0:14:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oman Lake
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.44,0:14:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再熱情點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.94,0:14:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oman Lake
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.54,0:14:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像在戀人耳邊低聲訴說情話那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.43,0:14:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oman Lake
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.91,0:14:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將要迎來高潮那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.99,0:14:26.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oman Lake
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.89,0:14:28.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像喝著黎明的咖啡時那樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.74,0:14:32.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.44,0:14:37.42,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去幫你跟老師請假 加油！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.43,0:14:36.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,律
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.43,0:14:38.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  律
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.84,0:14:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  繼續繼續…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.02,0:14:46.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好  這是色情小說家芥川丈途的手機
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.56,0:14:43.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36}又來!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.30,0:14:48.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如有催稿以外的要事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.86,0:14:51.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請在聽到嗶～的聲音後留言
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.77,0:14:52.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啵～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.72,0:14:54.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞定啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.00,0:14:57.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要隨便接別人的電話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.86,0:15:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.20,0:15:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我想我是你的經理人  所以就得意忘形了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.38,0:15:04.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  我這個笨蛋笨蛋笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.94,0:15:06.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再附贈個「笨蛋」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.97,0:15:08.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這孩子沒救了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.50,0:15:09.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這孩子沒救了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.58,0:15:16.87,Comment,NTP,0000,0110,0120,,{\fad(600,0)\an3\3c#000000\bord3.5}中午12點 : 26小時過後
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.12,0:15:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子好餓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.24,0:15:22.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小勝代嗎  門開著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.85,0:15:23.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.95,0:15:25.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.88,0:15:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謠江同學?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.45,0:15:33.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我聽說在修羅場的作家很辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.69,0:15:35.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就做便當帶過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.93,0:15:37.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你添麻煩了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.30,0:15:41.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒有那種事  剛好我肚子餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.30,0:15:45.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要看  太丟人了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.89,0:15:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為時間不太夠  有些著急…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.24,0:15:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謠江同學
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.74,0:15:52.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  畢竟她是偶像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.30,0:15:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明很忙  卻為了我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.58,0:15:59.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現役頂級偶像親手做的便當
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.33,0:16:02.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,配上手上纏的創可貼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.05,0:16:04.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.48,0:16:06.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.29,0:16:10.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到得到別人的支持會這麼讓人高興
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.91,0:16:12.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太誇張了  丈途同學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.78,0:16:13.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  快吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.01,0:16:17.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間不多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.58,0:16:20.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續寫稿吧  我來餵你吃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.63,0:16:21.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.00,0:16:23.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.83,0:16:27.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.45,0:16:31.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點不好意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.68,0:16:32.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.89,0:16:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  味道如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.19,0:16:39.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.19,0:16:40.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.40,0:16:41.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的真的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.78,0:16:44.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我至今為止吃過的最好吃的便當了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.90,0:16:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  太誇張了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.02,0:16:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼老師  加油寫稿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.86,0:16:51.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.30,0:16:54.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這雙筷子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.78,0:16:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼看都是謠江同學的私人物品
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.07,0:16:58.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也  也就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.29,0:17:01.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那雙嘴唇接觸了這雙筷子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.41,0:17:03.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這雙筷子又接觸了我的嘴唇…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.26,0:17:07.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就等於是  我的嘴唇和那雙嘴唇…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.71,0:17:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是現實的破壞力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.90,0:17:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行得通  把這份激情投入作品中去…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.78,0:17:17.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.30,0:17:22.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  被運動部的人拜託去給他們加油
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.53,0:17:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過已經結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.49,0:17:26.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好精緻的便當
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.24,0:17:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰做的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.25,0:17:31.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不介意的話  一起吃怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.26,0:17:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.64,0:17:35.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不好意思  我肚子都餓扁了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.78,0:17:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  繼續加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.70,0:17:40.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.51,0:17:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝款待
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.26,0:17:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.47,0:17:55.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明差一點就可以想到什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.31,0:17:57.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.39,0:17:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是完全沒有進展嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.97,0:18:01.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  還是完全沒有思路
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.37,0:18:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過還不用著急  還有20個小時呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.53,0:18:08.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一小時…那個…該寫多少頁好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.69,0:18:09.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.69,0:18:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要引出情慾  首先需要遮掩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.34,0:18:14.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後則需要若隱若現展露出來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.61,0:18:15.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是基本嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.13,0:18:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集中精神  用上我所有的感官
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.79,0:18:20.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我現在感受到的這份感情 現實的激情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.05,0:18:23.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次一定要把它們變成文字
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.88,0:18:28.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你偷看了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.22,0:18:31.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的  一不留神目光掃到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.94,0:18:33.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是為了作品吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.57,0:18:37.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讀了丈途同學的很多作品  所以我懂的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.53,0:18:40.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了作品創作  這種事是必要的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.08,0:18:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.82,0:18:50.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  不是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.07,0:18:52.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.96,0:18:57.93,Comment,NTP,0000,0110,0120,,{\fad(600,0)\an3\3c#000000\bord3.5}晚上9點 : 35小時過後
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.06,0:19:04.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還剩下12個小時
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.63,0:19:07.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原稿寫得怎麼樣了  完成了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.35,0:19:08.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全沒…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.28,0:19:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法了  接下來就是真正的修羅場了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.26,0:19:18.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從現在起  一分一秒目光也不能離開稿紙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.09,0:19:21.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼快寫吧  我也要加油
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.02,0:19:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fight oh! Fight oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.06,0:19:27.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go 丈途…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.48,0:19:27.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36}果然還是這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.14,0:19:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擦汗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.82,0:19:31.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  老師
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.20,0:19:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總感覺不對勁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.83,0:19:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手  手…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.36,0:19:42.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.93,0:19:44.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請賜予丈途同學的手以奇跡…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.99,0:19:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個也不對
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.47,0:19:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣  寫出來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.29,0:19:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  我已經沒法描寫女孩了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.55,0:19:59.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會  就連這套珍藏的服裝也不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.50,0:20:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經夠了  我已經打算封筆了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.11,0:20:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是不行的  丈途同學是天才色情小說家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.88,0:20:07.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不寫色情小說怎麼行…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.47,0:20:08.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.74,0:20:10.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以這麼放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.33,0:20:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.39,0:20:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被這樣綁著  我怎麼能寫得出來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.75,0:20:17.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但…但是我是經理人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.18,0:20:18.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經夠了  給我出去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.89,0:20:25.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.25,0:20:35.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是說過火了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.35,0:20:38.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過無所謂了  已經結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.19,0:20:40.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丈途同學
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.88,0:20:43.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這回我總算是明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.42,0:20:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是女生所以才寫不出來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.43,0:20:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我仔細想過了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.44,0:20:48.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.55,0:20:55.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天才肌肉同好會  高級健身家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.01,0:20:57.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,健美肌肉～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.37,0:21:01.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼各位  為了丈途同學的色情小說家之路
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.17,0:21:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盡情為他展示男人的美妙之處吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.05,0:21:05.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是肌肉男
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.29,0:21:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yoo 這是二頭肌
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.56,0:21:10.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yoo 這是腹肌
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.71,0:21:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是胸肌
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.04,0:21:14.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣  丈途同學
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.77,0:21:16.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碰到了  碰到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.50,0:21:21.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好硬  還很濕 而且好臭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.05,0:21:23.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請加油  芥川老師
